{"tid":494626,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《以青春的名義》暫時係今年睇過最有誠既香港作品！","createTime":"2017-12-09T19:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T16:55:33.000Z","uid":129019,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a40688a1be2702e04fd41edd4105f41bf9ec58e4","tid":494626,"uid":129019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T19:56:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uQXvG4LMGrM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuQXvG4LMGrM&d=N77O3Tm2IL4Pz41%2FRoyO25UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=47e17e48\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uQXvG4LMGrM</a><br />\n<br />\n可能近幾年大家都會只焦點去睇哂d社會題材，抽盡政治油水既本土作品，但去到今年已經油盡燈枯，但突然殺出呢套《以青春的名義》純粹講一段師生戀既故事，我就非常期待下，買到琴晚優先場，睇完後真係覺得終於有新導演肯踏踏實實去認真拍一個畸戀既故事，估唔到劉嘉玲會肯做呢個角色，男主角只係個中學生，竟然可以咁好戲，由頭帶到尾都可以咁壓場，做佢老豆個位竟然係武指董瑋，仲有一個影帝級既謝君豪釋演偷食局長，呢個組合每個人物都連環緊扣，故事好多呼應都做得好有感受，連d攝影同美術都係香港比較少見既高水準，如果個個新導演都可以拍到咁，香港未來電影界可以完全接班，但如果政府可以俾多d錢佢拍就真係重中之重喇，呢個新導演值得再期待<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog.hkmovie6.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Screen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-5.26.34-PM-1080x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.hkmovie6.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2FScreen-Shot-2017-09-25-at-5.26.34-PM-1080x0.png&h=c547c8fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8cc95227d2fe530e9700ddacdd11f5cc66174dd","tid":494626,"uid":19592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T20:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 期待咗好耐。"},{"pid":"6ef3ddf1428ef8d04d0a79a09690eee0105e260c","tid":494626,"uid":1408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:14:07.000Z","msg":"等左好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7b0673ec70f20eae79dbce091dc30d278d142d","tid":494626,"uid":129019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 期待咗好耐。</blockquote><br />\n仲有一個月唔